			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This is a must have spell.  In a group, this is almost always the only spell I cast.  I will cast once, send the pet in (if the group allows it), and maybe take a swing or two on my own.  This spell will match most mid level fighters just by itself.  Plus if I do 10-19 points a hit (with totem staff), then I am more than pulling my weight.  This also allows you to conserve mana for emergency situations so that you can engage in more combats.  In dungeon situations, cast this on NPC necros to slow get them dying quickly.  Nothing is worse then having to kill an NPC necro's horde of pets versus just it.
